projectGridLines.title: Business Development in Start-Up
projectGridLines.description:
Description: This project will engage students in different business development and marketing work for a start-up

Skill sets: Fluent English, basic soft skills, impressive extra-curricular activities, student with a holistic profile and not merely academically inclined

Traits expectation: Basic word and excel requirement

Expected learning: Students will learn the workings of start-up

Specific courses required for project execution: None
